name: Triple Time Killer Game
description:
JUMP! JETPACK! FLAP!

Yes, all of those are abilities you receive in this game as you try to miss objects while being pushed through the gameplay.

Black - Jetpack
White - Jump
Red - Flap

---** Diamond Button is Restore Purchase

No dealing with character locks

NO MORE ADS! WOOOHOO!

You can't keep up, this game is fast-paced and intense. You will be ranking up on the leaderboard while collecting coins and competing against friends to unlock fun new characters.

While this game will keep you on edge, you'll soon collect enough coins over time to unlock amazing characters!

Triple Time Killer Game is a great game to play on leaderboards with friends! This exciting gameplay will always keep you guessing by offering many different custom gameplay changes every time you press start. The entire time you're playing you also collect coins, unlocking new characters!
